    "created_at": "2015-04-13T06:08:33Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-04-13T06:08:33Z",
    "body": "Windows forbids overriding many <kbd>Win</kbd> global shortcuts, to override them the program has to install keyboard hooks or low level drivers, there is no normal way to work around the limitation.\n\nI'm closing this as won't fix.\n"
